{
  "stem": "4830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we immediately went there to help him up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said, for heaven's sake, what happened to you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, nothing, you crazy, I just put some soap into my mouth to stop this nonsense.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is how we lived in those days, which were relatively easy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Really nothing happened then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But on October the 10th, I-- I was-- my feelings were hurt by this beating up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't really like it at all and I decided that I discontinue my cooperation with the authorities, and we decided to leave.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we left on October the 10th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And first I was hiding in our apartment, in the place where-- that I already mentioned to you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then October 15th, the Governor Horthy read his declaration instating that the real enemy are the Germans, and he ordered the Hungarian military units to attack the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This did not really materialize in most places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my brother's unit, under the leadership of their so-called [INAUDIBLE]-- the-- the soldiers-- you know, their commander made a speech and said that we didn't really treat you well, but our supreme leader ordered everybody-- every member of the army to attack the Germans.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you are willing to follow me, I will lead you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was at the moment with my brother, and we had very few weapons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had the weapons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were leading us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just went there, and he spoke German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We surrounded a German military train in a neighboring railway station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told them that they are surrounded and they should surrender.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there was no exchange of any hostility.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We picked up all their arms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We told them to go back to Germany, and left them on the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
